    "lyrics": {
      "text": "The sol-diers stand-ing guard at Thy tomb, O my Sav-iour, be-came as dead on see-ing the light--ning-like An-gel who preached to the wom-en of Thine a-ris--ing, O Ho-ly Lord. Thee we glo-ri-fy, Who hast a-bol-ished cor-rup-tion; Thee do we a-dore, Who from the grave hast a-ris-en and Who a-lone art__ our__ God. \n\nand Who a-lone art__ our__ God.____"
    }
